HUONG DAN CHAY DU AN DA_AWS_FCAJ

Muc dich
--------
File nay huong dan cac thanh vien trong nhom chay du an Document Management + Security Monitoring tren may local.

Du an gom 2 phan:

1. Backend: Python Flask
2. Frontend: React + Vite

Backend ket noi AWS that:

- Amazon S3: luu file tai lieu
- DynamoDB Documents: luu metadata file
- DynamoDB SecurityIncidents: luu incident bao mat


1. Yeu cau truoc khi chay
-------------------------
Moi thanh vien can cai:

- Python 3.10 tro len
- Node.js 20 tro len
- npm
- AWS CLI
- Git

Kiem tra tren PowerShell:

python --version
node --version
npm --version
aws --version


2. Clone hoac mo source code
----------------------------
Neu clone tu GitHub:

git clone <repository-url>
cd da_aws_fcaj

Neu da co source san:

cd "D:\OneDrive\Máy tính\da_aws_fcaj"


3. Cau hinh AWS CLI
-------------------
Chay:

aws configure

Nhap thong tin IAM user cua nhom:

AWS Access Key ID: <access-key>
AWS Secret Access Key: <secret-key>
Default region name: ap-southeast-1
Default output format: json

Kiem tra dang nhap AWS:

aws sts get-caller-identity

Neu lenh nay tra ve Account va Arn la OK.


4. Tao file backend/.env
------------------------
Trong thu muc backend, tao file ten la:

.env

Co the copy tu .env.example:

copy backend\.env.example backend\.env

Noi dung mau:

AWS_REGION=ap-southeast-1
S3_BUCKET_NAME=da-aws-documents-caominhhuy-2280601128
DYNAMODB_DOCUMENTS_TABLE=Documents
DYNAMODB_INCIDENTS_TABLE=SecurityIncidents
JWT_SECRET_KEY=nhom5_secret_key_random_32_characters_2026
FLASK_DEBUG=0

Luu y:

- S3_BUCKET_NAME phai dung ten bucket AWS that.
- DYNAMODB_DOCUMENTS_TABLE phai dung ten table Documents.
- DYNAMODB_INCIDENTS_TABLE phai dung ten table SecurityIncidents.
- JWT_SECRET_KEY nen dai hon 32 ky tu.
- Khong commit file .env len GitHub.


5. Chay backend
---------------
Mo PowerShell tai thu muc goc du an:

cd "D:\OneDrive\Máy tính\da_aws_fcaj"

Vao thu muc backend:

cd backend

Tao virtual environment neu chua co:

python -m venv venv

Kich hoat virtual environment:

.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

Neu PowerShell chan script, chay:

Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1

Cai thu vien:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Chay backend:

python app.py

Neu thanh cong, backend chay tai:

http://127.0.0.1:5000


6. Test backend health
----------------------
Mo PowerShell moi, chay:

Invoke-RestMethod http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/health

Ket qua dung:

status: ok
backend: ok
s3: ok
documents_table: ok
incidents_table: ok

Neu status la degraded thi xem muc "Loi thuong gap" ben duoi.


7. Chay frontend
----------------
Mo PowerShell moi tai thu muc goc du an:

cd "D:\OneDrive\Máy tính\da_aws_fcaj"

Vao thu muc frontend:

cd frontend

Cai dependencies:

npm install

Chay frontend:

npm run dev

Neu thanh cong, frontend chay tai:

http://127.0.0.1:5173

Mo trinh duyet va truy cap dia chi tren.


8. Tai khoan dang nhap demo
---------------------------
Admin:

username: admin
password: admin123

User thuong:

username: user1
password: password1

Quyen khac nhau:

- admin: upload, download, delete document, xem incident, doi status incident
- user1: upload, download, xem document, xem incident, khong duoc delete document


9. Test chuc nang tai lieu
--------------------------
Dang nhap bang admin:

admin / admin123

Test upload:

1. Vao trang Upload
2. Chon file .pdf, .docx, .xlsx, .png, .jpg, .jpeg hoac .txt
3. Bam Upload
4. Neu thanh cong, quay ve Dashboard se thay file moi

Test download:

1. O Dashboard, bam Download tren file vua upload
2. Trinh duyet se mo/tai file bang presigned URL tu S3

Test delete:

1. Dang nhap admin
2. O Dashboard, bam Delete
3. File se bi xoa khoi S3 va metadata bi xoa khoi DynamoDB

Test phan quyen:

1. Logout
2. Dang nhap user1 / password1
3. Kiem tra nut Delete khong hien voi user thuong


10. Test incident
-----------------
Trang incident:

http://127.0.0.1:5173/incidents

Neu bang SecurityIncidents co du lieu, incident se hien tren giao dien.

De tao incident demo bang AWS CLI:

aws dynamodb put-item `
  --table-name SecurityIncidents `
  --region ap-southeast-1 `
  --item '{
    "incident_id": {"S": "demo-001"},
    "timestamp": {"S": "2026-07-10T10:00:00Z"},
    "finding_type": {"S": "UnauthorizedAccess:EC2/SSHBruteForce"},
    "severity": {"S": "HIGH"},
    "status": {"S": "OPEN"},
    "region": {"S": "ap-southeast-1"},
    "account_id": {"S": "demo-account"},
    "resource_id": {"S": "i-demo123"}
  }'

Sau do refresh trang Incidents.

Admin co the doi status:

- OPEN
- INVESTIGATING
- RESOLVED


11. Test bang API nhanh
-----------------------
Test login:

Invoke-RestMethod `
  -Method Post `
  -Uri http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/login `
  -ContentType "application/json" `
  -Body '{"username":"admin","password":"admin123"}'

Test health:

Invoke-RestMethod http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/health


12. Build frontend de kiem tra production
-----------------------------------------
Trong thu muc frontend:

npm run build

Neu build thanh cong, thu muc dist se duoc tao.


13. Loi thuong gap
------------------
Loi: Cannot upload document to AWS

Nguyen nhan thuong gap:

- S3 bucket sai ten trong backend/.env
- IAM user chua co quyen S3
- AWS CLI chua configure dung credential
- Backend chua restart sau khi sua .env

Cach kiem tra:

aws s3api head-bucket --bucket da-aws-documents-caominhhuy-2280601128 --region ap-southeast-1

Neu lenh tren thanh cong, se tra ve:

AccessPointAlias: false

Sau do restart backend.


Loi: s3 ok false trong /api/health

Kiem tra:

- Bucket co ton tai khong
- Bucket co dung region ap-southeast-1 khong
- IAM user/role co quyen s3:ListBucket, s3:PutObject, s3:GetObject, s3:DeleteObject khong


Loi: documents_table ok false

Kiem tra:

- DynamoDB table Documents da tao chua
- Table co trang thai Active chua
- Ten trong .env co dung khong
- IAM user co quyen DynamoDB khong


Loi: incidents_table ok false

Kiem tra:

- DynamoDB table SecurityIncidents da tao chua
- Table co trang thai Active chua
- Ten trong .env co dung khong
- IAM user co quyen DynamoDB khong


Loi: npm khong chay duoc

Thu dung:

npm.cmd install
npm.cmd run dev

Neu node khong ton tai:

- Cai Node.js LTS
- Dong va mo lai PowerShell


Loi: port 5000 da duoc su dung

Kiem tra process:

Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 5000 -State Listen | Select-Object LocalAddress,LocalPort,State,OwningProcess

Dung process:

Stop-Process -Id <OwningProcess> -Force


14. Thu tu chay moi lan lam viec
--------------------------------
Moi lan muon chay du an:

Terminal 1 - Backend:

cd "D:\OneDrive\Máy tính\da_aws_fcaj\backend"
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
python app.py

Terminal 2 - Frontend:

cd "D:\OneDrive\Máy tính\da_aws_fcaj\frontend"
npm run dev

Mo trinh duyet:

http://127.0.0.1:5173


15. Checklist truoc khi demo
----------------------------
- Backend dang chay o port 5000
- Frontend dang chay o port 5173
- /api/health tra status ok
- Dang nhap admin thanh cong
- Upload file thanh cong
- File hien trong S3
- Metadata hien trong DynamoDB Documents
- Download file thanh cong
- Trang /incidents doc duoc du lieu tu SecurityIncidents
- User thuong khong co quyen delete


16. Lien ket voi kien truc AWS
------------------------------
Phan backend/frontend hien tai di theo luong:

User
-> React Frontend
-> Flask Backend
-> Amazon S3
-> DynamoDB Documents

Phan incident di theo luong:

GuardDuty / Security Hub
-> EventBridge
-> Lambda Incident Response
-> DynamoDB SecurityIncidents
-> Flask Backend /api/incidents
-> React Frontend /incidents

Neu nhom Security chua lam Lambda, co the tao incident demo bang tay trong DynamoDB de test frontend/backend.
